OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fin the morning, falling a sleet over
OL,7,FShetland. Drier by the afternoon with
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA cloudy evening for Orkney
OL,11,Fwith some rain but brighter over
OL,12,FShetland. Clear spells and showers
OL,13,Fovernight, these falling as sleet or
OL,14,Fhail at times. Strengthening
OL,15,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA mixture of sunshine and
OL,18,Fblustery showers, heavy and wintry at
OL,19,Ftimes. Feeling unseasonably cold with
OL,20,Fa fresh northwesterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
