OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Ftouch of frost early Wednesday then
OL,7,Fmainly dry and bright, but showers
OL,8,Farriving later. Rain or showers
OL,9,FThursday and Friday. Feeling rather
OL,10,Fcool for the time of year.
